This paper focuses on using artificial intelligence tools, specifically sentiment analysis techniques, to analyze textual content in online reviews and understand the relationship between the text and the assigned numerical score. This falls under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and cybernetics (cs.CY).
